#   Revision history for RT-Extension-MandatoryFields


##  0.6 (Fri, 07 Jun 2013 14:27:22 +0200)

*   Allow the setting of a list of queue indeces where the field is mandatory (thanks to Davide Imbeni)
*   Also allow to use the keyword 'all' with the same effect as 'true' (Davide)
*   Added Italian translation (Davide)
*   Updated to Module::Install 1.06 (thanks to Tatsuhiko Miyagawa)


##  0.5 (Tue, 03 Jan 2012 09:53:08 +0100)

*   Added Spanish and Catalan translations
*   Localize field names


##  0.4 (Tue, 20 Dec 2011 12:40:16 +0100)

*   Added priority field
*   Added German translation
*   Cleaned up code


##  0.3 (Tue, 29 Nov 2011 11:08:11 +0100)

*   More supported fields
*   Updated installation routines
*   Improved meta information
*   Enhanced documentation (now POD only)


##  0.2 (Thu, 17 Nov 2011 15:11:23 +0100)

*   Re-packaging


##  0.1.1 (Thu, 17 Nov 2011 13:44:19 +0100)

*   Added SIGNATURE; improved meta information


##  0.1 (Tue, 15 Nov 2011 10:07:47 +0100)

*   Initial release.
